  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/f7b09521b683c2be27554372ab00d071.poster.avif?t=1739470757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/f7b09521b683c2be27554372ab00d071.webm?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/f7b09521b683c2be27554372ab00d071.mp4?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DESCENT</strong> is a movement based shooter inspired by early source bunny-hopping and surfing found in games like QUAKE and Counter-Strike. You play as the champion of Hermes, tasked with traversing through many dimensions to find artefacts in order to save your home realm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/7e603660d3a579965c39669c7b3f3c67.poster.avif?t=1739470757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/7e603660d3a579965c39669c7b3f3c67.webm?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/7e603660d3a579965c39669c7b3f3c67.mp4?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Bunnyhop</i></strong> through landscapes inspired by various mythologies with an low res, old school aesthetic with music tracks produced by <strong><u>Trashiii</u></strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use various movement mechanics such as <strong><i>Bunnyhopping</i></strong>, <strong><i>Surfing</i></strong> and <strong><i>Grappling</i></strong> to mix up your gameplay. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Speedrun</i></strong> through each level to get the best time on the online <strong><u>leaderboards</u></strong>! Compete against everyone or just your friends.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/785525837c0bcfaa663a604a01d62633.poster.avif?t=1739470757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/785525837c0bcfaa663a604a01d62633.webm?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/785525837c0bcfaa663a604a01d62633.mp4?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/f7b09521b683c2be27554372ab00d071.poster.avif?t=1739470757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/f7b09521b683c2be27554372ab00d071.webm?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/f7b09521b683c2be27554372ab00d071.mp4?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DESCENT</strong> is a movement based shooter inspired by early source bunny-hopping and surfing found in games like QUAKE and Counter-Strike. You play as the champion of Hermes, tasked with traversing through many dimensions to find artefacts in order to save your home realm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/7e603660d3a579965c39669c7b3f3c67.poster.avif?t=1739470757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/7e603660d3a579965c39669c7b3f3c67.webm?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/7e603660d3a579965c39669c7b3f3c67.mp4?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Bunnyhop</i></strong> through landscapes inspired by various mythologies with an low res, old school aesthetic with music tracks produced by <strong><u>Trashiii</u></strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use various movement mechanics such as <strong><i>Bunnyhopping</i></strong>, <strong><i>Surfing</i></strong> and <strong><i>Grappling</i></strong> to mix up your gameplay. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Speedrun</i></strong> through each level to get the best time on the online <strong><u>leaderboards</u></strong>! Compete against everyone or just your friends.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/785525837c0bcfaa663a604a01d62633.poster.avif?t=1739470757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/785525837c0bcfaa663a604a01d62633.webm?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755240/extras/785525837c0bcfaa663a604a01d62633.mp4?t=1739470757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
